<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.7.1">
<l>aṅkaṇ ñāla mañcavaṅkō rāḷari yāyavuṇaṉ</l>
<l>poṅka vākam vaḷḷukirāl pōḻntapu ṉitaṉiṭam</l>
<l>paiṅka ṇāṉaik kompukoṇṭu pattimai yālaṭikkīḻc</l>
<l>ceṅka ṇāḷi yiṭṭiṟaiñcuñ ciṅkavēḷ kuṉṟamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the pure one, who once as a man-lion,</l>
<l rend="indent">split with sharp claws the chest of the demon</l>
<l>As [he] raged, while the world of lovely places trembled,</l>
<l>Is Lion-Man Mountain where red-eyed lions,</l>
<l rend="indent">bearing tusks of green-eyed elephants,</l>
<l>Bow, laying [them] with devotion low at [his] feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
